feat: bridge task persistence, heartbeat, stall detection

Queue persistence:
- Persist instructionQueue to globalState (survives restarts)
- On startup: load queue, reset processing/stalled tasks to pending
- All queue mutations (enqueue, process, remove, clear) now persist

Heartbeat and stall detection:
- POST /ai/queue/:id/heartbeat — keepalive for processing tasks
- Stall detection loop: processing with no heartbeat for 5min → stalled
- Auto re-queue: stalled for 10min → reset to pending and re-dispatch
- New status: 'stalled' added to QueueInstruction

New endpoints:
- GET /ai/queue/pending — tasks not yet finalized
- GET /ai/queue/stalled — tasks with expired heartbeat
- POST /ai/queue/:id/heartbeat — record keepalive

Response queue:
- Accept 'in-progress' status for task acknowledgment on pickup
- Stats now include stalled count
